GraphData.Name: Move Z Collimator with end of seam marker
GraphData.Kommentar: Moves Z collimator to input position, when position is reached. Needs Z pos input in mm (e.g. from IDM) and Position reached Signal. Sends end of seam marker as soon position is reached.
